Author: punchjackal
Text: God, yes. I've rediscovered my love for Food Network and found myself getting obsessed with terrible cooking videos (Kay's Cooking, Cooking With Hoarders, etc.) Watching people eat is one thing, but watching people cook does it for me like no other.  Eugh, the way I talk about media that fuels my ED makes me feel like a middle aged dude talking about his fetishes.
